    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iesu Christi Dei aeterni. <persName
                            key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/9">Hlotharius</persName> divina
                        ordinante providentia <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> Augustus.
                        Quicquid enim divino amore tacti locis Deo dicatis conferimus, id nobis
                        aeternis conpendiis recompensari minime dubitamus. Igitur cunctorum fidelium
                        sanctae Dei Ecclesiae nostrorumque cognoscat sollertia, quia nos pro
                        mercedis nostrae aucmento ob amore Dei et venerabilis <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/47">sancti
                            Silvestri</orgName> tacti in <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/15">Nonantulas</placeName> in <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">pabulo</rs> et quascumque alias necessitates
                        subplendas perenniter possidendum contulimus quandam <rs key="#Islands"
                            >insulam</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Islands #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/1539">Viciana</placeName> nomine consistentem inter <rs
                            key="#Rivers">Padum et Bondinum</rs> in integrum, ita ut ibidem Deo
                        famulantes in utilitates eiusdem monasterii <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">perenniter
                            teneant atque faciant quicquid voluerint</rs>. Unde pro firmitatis
                        gratia circa eundem sanctum locum has nostras litteras fieri iussimus, per
                        quas praecipimus, ut nemo quislibet ex fidelium nostrorum inde quippiam
                        repetitionis parti praescripti monasterii inferre praesumat, sed omni in
                        tempore quieto ordine teneant atque quoque haec nostra auctoritas pleniorem
                        obtineat vigorem, manu propria subter eam firmavimus et anuli nostri
                        inpressione adsignari iussimus. Signum MF Hlotharii gloriosissimi augusti.
                            <persName key="#Notary #Subdeacons" ref="#people/3906"
                            >Dructemirus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Subdeacons">subdiaconus</rs> atque <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>
                        ad vicem <persName ref="#people/1235">Egilmari</persName> recognovi et SR NT
                        SID Data VI kalendas februarii, anno Christo propitio Imperii Hlothari pii
                        imperatoris XVIII, indictione XV. Actum <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                        <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Residential #Palatium"
                            ref="#places/20"><geogName ref="#estates/247"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Function #Residential #Palatium"
                                >Auriola</geogName></placeName>
                        <rs key="#Palatium">palatio regio</rs>; in Dei nomine NT.</ab>
